ClipBucket License Agreement

What is CBLA (ClipBucket License Agreement):-

The CBLA (ClipBucket License Agreement) is, as its name shows it, a contract between the software developer/Owner (Arslan Hassan / PHPBucket / ClipBucket / ClipBucket Lite) and a potential user/You(Either an Entity or a Single User). By means of this contract it is established that the developer of the software is its de facto owner, and that a copy of the respective software Downloaded from a vendor (or downloaded from the Internet) only licenses it to a user, and does not transmit any intellectual rights whatsoever on the Software. The end user is only allowed to use it as long as certain terms are respected, and is also prohibited from any alterations or uses of the software without the specific consent of its rightful owner, the software company/developer(ClipBucket / PHPBucket ). 

